<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="container header-content">
            <a href="/" class="logo">Common<span class="highlight"><span class="cent-sign">C</span>ents</span></a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="page-content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>At CommonCents, we believe that every cent counts. Our mission is to help you discover the best deals across the web, saving you time and money on everything from tech gadgets to household essentials.</p>
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>We curate and share the most valuable deals from across the internet, covering categories like:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Tech:</strong> Laptops, smartphones, headphones, and more</li>
            <li><strong>Tools:</strong> Power tools, DIY equipment, and hardware</li>
            <li><strong>Household:</strong> Home essentials, appliances, and cleaning supplies</li>
            <li><strong>Credit Cards:</strong> Best signup bonuses and rewards programs</li>

        </ul>
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>Our team scours the internet daily to find legitimate deals that offer real value. We verify prices, check availability, and only feature offers that meet our quality standards. When you click on a deal link, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
        <h2>Community-Driven</h2>
        <p>We also welcome deal submissions from our community. If you spot an amazing deal, submit it through our "Submit a Deal" feature, and we'll review it for inclusion on the site.</p>
        <h2>Transparency</h2>
        <p>We're committed to transparency. All affiliate relationships are clearly disclosed, and we never let affiliate partnerships influence which deals we recommend. If it's not a good deal, we won't share it.</p>
        <h2>Stay Updated</h2>
        <p>Subscribe to our newsletter to get the best deals delivered straight to your inbox. We promise never to spam you – just quality deals, delivered daily.</p>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you. Visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to get in touch.</p>
    </div>
    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="container footer-content">
